rong language! Hope you enjoy!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/747340/extras/8f08d06456135ac566847876c7689567.avif?t=1625813197\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
